# Android WMS 应用启动窗口完整流程详解

## 📋 概述

当用户启动一个应用时，Android 系统会经过多个阶段完成窗口的创建、添加、焦点设置和最终绘制显示。下面详细分析整个流程。

---

## 一、窗口创建准备阶段（Activity 启动）

### 1.1 AMS 通知应用进程启动 Activity

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/am/ActivityTaskManagerService.java`
- `frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/am/ActivityStackSupervisor.java`

**流程：**
1. **AMS**（ActivityManagerService）收到启动 Activity 的请求
2. 通过 Binder 调用通知 **ActivityTaskManagerService**（ATMS）
3. ATMS 创建 **ActivityRecord** 表示该 Activity
4. 通过 **ApplicationThread**（一个 Binder 服务）向应用进程发送启动消息

### 1.2 ActivityThread 创建 Activity

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/core/java/android/app/ActivityThread.java`

```java
// ActivityThread.java - performLaunchActivity()
private Activity performLaunchActivity(ActivityClientRecord r, Intent customIntent) {
    // 1. 创建 Activity 对象
    activity = mInstrumentation.newActivity(cl, component.getClassName(), intent);

    // 2. 调用 attach() - 关键：创建 PhoneWindow
    activity.attach(appContext, this, token, ...);

    // 3. 调用 onCreate()
    mInstrumentation.callActivityOnCreate(activity, r.state);

    return activity;
}
```

### 1.3 Activity.attach() 创建 PhoneWindow

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/core/java/android/app/Activity.java`

```java
// Activity.java - attach()
final void attach(...) {
    // 创建 PhoneWindow（Activity 的唯一窗口实现）
    mWindow = new PhoneWindow(this, windowContext);

    // 设置 Window 回调
    mWindow.setWindowManager(
        (WindowManager)context.getSystemService(Context.WINDOW_SERVICE),
        mToken, mDisplay.getPackageName(), ...);
}
```

### 1.4 setContentView() 创建 DecorView

**流程：**
1. `Activity.setContentView(layoutResID)` 被调用
2. 创建 **DecorView**（根视图容器）
3. 将布局 inflate 到 DecorView 的 mContentParent 中
4. `mWindow.setContentView()` 完成视图树构建

---

## 二、窗口注册阶段（向 WMS 添加窗口）

### 2.1 handleResumeActivity 触发窗口添加

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/core/java/android/app/ActivityThread.java`

```java
// ActivityThread.java - handleResumeActivity()
public void handleResumeActivity(IBinder token, ...) {
    // 1. 调用 onResume()
    activity.performResume();

    // 2. 获取 WindowManager 并添加 DecorView
    ViewManager wm = a.getWindowManager();
    wm.addView(decor, l);  // 👈 关键入口
}
```

### 2.2 WindowManagerImpl.addView()

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/core/java/android/view/WindowManagerImpl.java`

```java
// WindowManagerImpl.java
public void addView(View view, ViewGroup.LayoutParams params) {
    // 添加到全局视图列表
    mViews.add(view);
    mParams.add(params);

    // 创建 ViewRootImpl 并调用 setView()
    root = new ViewRootImpl(context, display);
    root.setView(view, params, ...);
}
```

### 2.3 ViewRootImpl.setView() 发起添加请求

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/core/java/android/view/ViewRootImpl.java`

```java
// ViewRootImpl.java - setView()
public void setView(View view, ViewGroup.LayoutParams attrs, ...) {
    synchronized (this) {
        // 1. 保存 DecorView 引用
        mView = view;

        // 2. 通过 IWindowSession 向 WMS 添加窗口
        res = mWindowSession.addToDisplay(mWindow, seq, mWindowAttributes,
            getHostVisibility(), ..., mInputChannel, mTempInsets);

        // 3. 发起首次布局请求
        requestLayout();
    }
}
```

### 2.4 WMS.addWindow() 服务端处理

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/wm/WindowManagerService.java`

**关键步骤：**

```java
// WMS.java - addWindow()
public int addWindow(Session session, IWindow client, 
                      WindowManager.LayoutParams attrs, ...) {
    // 1. 权限检查
    int res = mPolicy.checkAddPermission(attrs);

    synchronized(mWindowMap) {
        // 2. 创建/获取 WindowToken
        WindowToken token = mTokenMap.get(attrs.token);
        if (token == null) {
            token = new WindowToken(this, attrs.token, attrs.type, ...);
            mTokenMap.put(attrs.token, token);
        }

        // 3. 创建 WindowState（窗口在 WMS 侧的表示）
        WindowState win = new WindowState(session, client, token, ...);

        // 4. 挂载到 WindowToken
        token.windows.add(win);
        mWindowMap.put(client.asBinder(), win);

        // 5. 调用 attach() 建立 Binder 连接
        win.attach();
    }

    return res;
}
```

---

## 三、Surface 创建阶段（relayoutWindow）

### 3.1 ViewRootImpl.requestLayout()

```java
// ViewRootImpl.java
public void requestLayout() {
    if (!mHandlingLayoutInLayoutRequest) {
        scheduleTraversals();  // 发送遍历消息
    }
}
```

### 3.2 ViewRootImpl.relayoutWindow()

```java
// ViewRootImpl.java
public int relayoutWindow(LayoutParams attrs, int requestedWidth, 
                          int requestedHeight, ...) {
    // 通过 Binder 调用 WMS
    int relayoutResult = mWindowSession.relayout(
        mWindow, seq, attrs, requestedWidth, requestedHeight,
        viewVisibility, flags, ..., mSurface);

    return relayoutResult;
}
```

### 3.3 WMS.relayoutWindow() 分配 Surface

**关键逻辑：**

```java
// WMS.java - relayoutWindow()
public int relayoutWindow(Session session, IWindow client, ...) {
    synchronized(mWindowMap) {
        WindowState win = mWindowMap.get(client.asBinder());

        // 1. 创建/获取 SurfaceControl
        SurfaceControl surfaceControl = win.getSurfaceControl();
        if (surfaceControl == null) {
            surfaceControl = new SurfaceControl.Builder()
                .setName(win.getAttrs().getTitle())
                .build();
            win.setSurfaceControl(surfaceControl);
        }

        // 2. 计算窗口布局
        performLayoutLocked();

        // 3. 返回给客户端
        outSurfaceControl.copyFrom(surfaceControl);
    }
}
```

---

## 四、焦点窗口设置

### 4.1 WMS.setFocusedWindow()

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/wm/WindowManagerService.java`

```java
// WMS.java
public int setFocusedWindow(IBinder token) {
    synchronized (mWindowMap) {
        WindowState newFocus = null;

        // 查找新的焦点窗口
        for (WindowState ws : mWindowMap.values()) {
            if (ws.mToken == token && ws.isVisibleNow()) {
                newFocus = ws;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (mCurrentFocus != newFocus) {
            // 通知旧焦点窗口失去焦点
            if (mCurrentFocus != null) {
                mCurrentFocus.mClient.windowFocusChanged(false, ...);
            }

            // 设置新焦点窗口
            mCurrentFocus = newFocus;

            // 通知新焦点窗口获得焦点
            if (newFocus != null) {
                newFocus.mClient.windowFocusChanged(true, ...);
            }
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
```

### 4.2 焦点变化通知客户端

```java
// IWindow.aidl (接口)
void windowFocusChanged(boolean hasFocus, int isInTouchMode);
```

---

## 五、绘制与显示

### 5.1 ViewRootImpl 绘制流程

```java
// ViewRootImpl.java - performTraversals()
private void performTraversals() {
    // 1. 测量 (Measure)
    measure(mWidth, mHeight);

    // 2. 布局 (Layout)  
    layout(mLeft, mTop, mRight, mBottom);

    // 3. 绘制 (Draw)
    draw(fullRedrawNeeded);
}
```

### 5.2 draw() 绘制到 Surface

```java
// ViewRootImpl.java - draw()
private void draw(boolean fullRedrawNeeded) {
    Canvas canvas;

    // 获取 Surface 的 Canvas
    canvas = mSurface.lockCanvas(dirty);

    try {
        // 调用 DecorView.draw() 绘制视图树
        mView.draw(canvas);
    } finally {
        // 解锁并提交
        mSurface.unlockCanvasAndPost(canvas);
    }
}
```

### 5.3 SurfaceFlinger 合成显示

```
应用进程                          系统进程                        硬件
   │                                 │                            │
   │  Surface 操作                   │                            │
   │ ─────────────────────────────►   │                            │
   │                                 │                            │
   │                                 │  BufferQueue + ANativeWindow │
   │                                 │ ──────────────────────────►  │
   │                                 │                            │
   │                                 │        硬件合成              │
   │                                 │ ◄──────────────────────────│
   │                                 │                            │
   │  显示完成通知                    │                            │
   │ ◄───────────────────────────────│                            │
```

---

## 六、关键数据结构关系

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Activity {
        +mWindow: PhoneWindow
        +mToken: IBinder
    }

    class PhoneWindow {
        +mDecor: DecorView
        +mWindowManager: WindowManagerImpl
    }

    class DecorView {
        +mContentParent: ViewGroup
    }

    class ViewRootImpl {
        +mView: View
        +mWindowSession: IWindowSession
        +mSurface: Surface
    }

    class WindowState {
        +mSession: Session
        +mClient: IWindow
        +mToken: WindowToken
        +mWinAnimator: WindowStateAnimator
        +mSurfaceControl: SurfaceControl
    }

    class AppWindowToken {
        +windows: ArrayList~WindowState~
        +appToken: IApplicationToken
    }

    class WindowToken {
        +token: IBinder
        +windows: ArrayList~WindowState~
    }

    Activity o-- PhoneWindow
    PhoneWindow o-- DecorView
    DecorView o-- ViewRootImpl
    ViewRootImpl ..> WindowState
    WindowState o-- AppWindowToken
    WindowState o-- WindowToken
```

---

## 七、完整时序图

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant AMS as AMS/ATMS
    participant AT as ActivityThread
    participant WM as WindowManager
    participant VR as ViewRootImpl
    participant WMS as WMS
    participant SF as SurfaceFlinger

    User->>AMS: startActivity()
    AMS->>AT: ApplicationThread.bindApplication()
    AT->>AT: performLaunchActivity()
    AT->>AT: activity.attach()
    AT->>AT: 创建 PhoneWindow
    AT->>AT: setContentView()

    AT->>AT: handleResumeActivity()
    AT->>WM: addView(DecorView)
    WM->>VR: new ViewRootImpl()
    VR->>VR: setView()

    VR->>WMS: IWindowSession.addToDisplay()
    WMS->>WMS: 创建 WindowState
    WMS->>WMS: 创建 AppWindowToken
    WMS-->>VR: ADD_OKAY

    VR->>VR: requestLayout()
    VR->>VR: scheduleTraversals()
    VR->>WMS: relayoutWindow()
    WMS->>WMS: 分配 Surface
    WMS-->>VR: Surface + FrameInfo

    VR->>VR: performTraversals()
    VR->>VR: measure()
    VR->>VR: layout()
    VR->>VR: draw()
    VR->>VR: mSurface.unlockCanvasAndPost()

    VR->>WMS: finishDrawing()
    WMS->>WMS: setFocusedWindow()
