### 3.3 WMS.relayoutWindow() 分配 Surface

**关键逻辑：**

```java
// WMS.java - relayoutWindow()
public int relayoutWindow(Session session, IWindow client, ...) {
    synchronized(mWindowMap) {
        WindowState win = mWindowMap.get(client.asBinder());

        // 1. 创建/获取 SurfaceControl
        SurfaceControl surfaceControl = win.getSurfaceControl();
        if (surfaceControl == null) {
            surfaceControl = new SurfaceControl.Builder()
                .setName(win.getAttrs().getTitle())
                .build();
            win.setSurfaceControl(surfaceControl);
        }

        // 2. 计算窗口布局
        performLayoutLocked();

        // 3. 返回给客户端
        outSurfaceControl.copyFrom(surfaceControl);
    }
}
