## 四、焦点窗口设置

### 4.1 WMS.setFocusedWindow()

**源码路径（AOSP master）：**
- `frameworks/base/services/core/java/com/android/server/wm/WindowManagerService.java`

```java
// WMS.java
public int setFocusedWindow(IBinder token) {
    synchronized (mWindowMap) {
        WindowState newFocus = null;

        // 查找新的焦点窗口
        for (WindowState ws : mWindowMap.values()) {
            if (ws.mToken == token && ws.isVisibleNow()) {
                newFocus = ws;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (mCurrentFocus != newFocus) {
            // 通知旧焦点窗口失去焦点
            if (mCurrentFocus != null) {
                mCurrentFocus.mClient.windowFocusChanged(false, ...);
            }

            // 设置新焦点窗口
            mCurrentFocus = newFocus;

            // 通知新焦点窗口获得焦点
            if (newFocus != null) {
                newFocus.mClient.windowFocusChanged(true, ...);
            }
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
```

